For anyone that has not read my article:

http://www.ratwell.com/technical/VDOGauges.html

I've tested all of popular VDO gauges and senders and they have near  
worthless accuracy. Their main value lies in the fact that you are  
able to compare inaccurate readings with someone else who has them!

Buy them for looks or to supplement your alternator/generator light. :-)

